---
import CardLinkRectangle from '../components/CardLinkRectangle.astro'
import CTAButton from '../components/CTAButton.astro'
import TestimonyCard from '../components/TestimonyCard.astro'
import TrustNumbers from '../components/TrustNumbers.astro'
import Wrapper from '../components/Wrapper.astro'
import CertificateIcon from '../icons/CertificateIcon.astro'
import HeartHearIcon from '../icons/HeartHearIcon.astro'
---

<Wrapper classname="grid-wrapper">

    <header class="heading-icon h-grid-one">
        <HeartHearIcon />
        <h2>¡Acelera tu carrera de medicina!</h2>
    </header>

    <section class="trust-container">
        <TrustNumbers num="600" title="Clases impartidas" />
        <TrustNumbers num="36" title="Medicos" />
        <TrustNumbers num="90" title="Simulacros" />
    </section>

    <section class="companies description-one">
        <p>Creemos firmemente que el acompañamiento es clave para el éxito de tu carrera académica.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="grid card-one">
        <CardLinkRectangle title="Clases de apoyo en Medicina" path="img/apoyo.webp" desc="Cursado de apoyo en medicina" className="rect"/>
    </section>

    <header class="heading-icon h-grid-two">
        <CertificateIcon />
        <h2>¡No pierdas tu progreso!</h2>
    </header>

    <section class="companies description-two">
        <p>Solicita la reválida y mantén viva tu oportunidad de rendir el final. Gestiona tus trámites académicos  y mantenete en camino.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="grid card-two">
        <CardLinkRectangle title="Revalidación y Tramites académicos" path="img/revalida.jpg" className="rect" />
    </section>

    <section class="heading-icon h-grid-three">
        <h2>Experiencias de estudiantes</h2>
    </section>

    <section class="testimonies">
        <TestimonyCard path="img/autor1.png">
            <Fragment slot="quote">
                Las clases son excelentes a nivel profesional al igual que los docentes, super cálidos, amables y dispuestos a enseñarte hasta que aprendas de verdad
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="author">
                María G.
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="role">
                Egresada en Marketing
            </Fragment>
        </TestimonyCard>
    </section>

    <footer class="button">
        <CTAButton text="Quiero acelerar mi carrera"/>
    </footer>

</Wrapper>

<style>
    .heading-icon {
        text-align: center;
    }

    .trust-container {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .companies {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        text-align: center;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
    }
    .companies small {
        font-weight: 600;
    }
    .logos {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 1.25rem;
    }

    .row {
        display: flex;
        gap: 0.75rem;
    }

    .grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 0.75rem;
    }


    h2, p {
        margin: 0;
    }


    @media screen and (max-width: 400px) {
        .grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
    }

    @media screen and (min-width: 850px) {
        .grid {
            grid-template-columns: auto;
        }
        .mobile-wrapper {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
        }


        .h-grid-one {
            grid-column: 1/3;
            grid-row: 1;

            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;

            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .h-grid-two {
            grid-column: 3/5;

            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;

            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .h-grid-three {
            grid-column: 1/5;

            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;

            font-size: 1.5rem;

        }
        .trust-container {
            grid-column: 1/5;
            grid-row: 3;
        }
        .description-one {
            grid-column: 1/3;
            grid-row: 2;
        }
        .description-two {
            grid-column: 3/5;
        }
        .description-one p, .description-two p {
            max-width: 42ch;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-inline: auto;
        }
        .card-one {
            grid-column: 3/5;
            grid-row: 1/3;
        }
        .card-two {
            grid-column: 1/3;
            grid-row: 4/6;
        }
        .last-card {
            grid-column: 3;
            grid-row: 1;
        }
        .testimonies {
            grid-column: 2/4;
        }
        .button {
            grid-column: 2/4;
        }
    }

</style>